dct_title_s: Sketch map of Eastern Turkistan to illustrate the paper by R. B. Shaw, Esqre
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Rivers and major mountain passes are shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 46 (1876), pp. 277-98; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v. 46 1876
